===Noun===
{{en-noun|s|-}}

# (''countable'') A pursuit or activity with rules performed either alone or with others, for the purpose of entertainment. 
#:''Shall we play a '''game'''?''<!-- - WOPR computer, from the movie ''[[w:Wargames|Wargames]]''.-->
